{"tid":2001423,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[勿急落order] 新MacBook 13頂配款同基礎款係兩部機","createTime":"2020-05-04T13:37:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-09T10:44:19.000Z","uid":4672,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"7f68be2cef066f7f359bf5e2765c56af606ce14e","tid":2001423,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T13:37:46.000Z","msg":"頂配款13999起步 用既係10代intel 10nm CPU<br />\n基礎款係 i5-8279U 14nm+<br />\n頂配款係 i7-1068NG7  10nm<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WUwVDOC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWUwVDOC.jpg&h=f26c80f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nCore i5-8279U與i7-1068NG7相似，但實際效能卻截然不同。i7-1068NG7在3DMark Time Spy中的圖形分數達到了846，較i5-8279U高了29.2%，CPU分數達到了3876，較Core i5-8279U高了12.1%。<br />\n<br />\n從測試結果可以看出，MacBook Pro 2020所搭載的10nm Ice Lake處理器於IPC效能方面的確要好於14nm的產品，特別是圖形效能，3DMark Time Spy的圖形分數可以與滿血版的MX150媲美，較前代的MacBook Pro 2019則是強了30%左右。<br />\n<br />\n順帶一提 搭載八代cpu MacBook pro 記憶體係 LPDDR3 2133mhz<br />\n而搭載10代CPU款 RAM係 LPDDR4X 3733MHz"},{"pid":"97450341cb75032a5a2b984aa31515d24308b55f","tid":2001423,"uid":4672,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T13:41:41.000Z","msg":"基礎款係8代u 19年Q2出<br />\n姐係係上年19機用剩<br />\n等睇幫apple清存貨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b0a42dc130a5898d345945fe481a109d1669b29","tid":2001423,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T13:47:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3fcadd6e6afbc6962a034cc4dca05b0e1d54f44","tid":2001423,"uid":75044,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T14:23:07.000Z","msg":"說好的14寸MBP呢？<br />\n又要等多年？？"},{"pid":"092b0b5443ebe95922050926591385a2d2ed682c","tid":2001423,"uid":99700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,